Package: equalizer
Version: 0.2.0
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: Tsiry Sandratraina <tsiry.sndr@rocksky.app>
Homepage: https://github.com/tsirysndr/equalizer
Depends: libc6, libasound2
Description: A real-time terminal equalizer for raw PCM pipes
 equalizer reads raw PCM from stdin, a FIFO, or a unix socket, runs it
 through the Rockbox DSP (10-band EQ, bass/treble shelves, resampling)
 and plays the result on your sound card — while a Synthwave '84 ratatui
 interface lets you tweak the bands live. Settings persist to a TOML
 file in Rockbox's own eq_band_settings format.
